descriptionShort: Our dinner sets make it easy to stock your kitchen cabinets with dinnerware you truly love.
descriptionLong: With 4 pieces of each variation, it's perfect for parties of 2 to 4. Bigger families, dinner party hosts, and those that want to skip the dishes once in a while will want to grab a few more sets.
